This paper discusses the implementation of a digital library based on metadata aggregation using Dublin Core and OAI-PMH. Therefore, it is most likely to belong to the arXiv categories of Digital Libraries (cs.DL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Library Science (cs.LIB). Additionally, the paper also discusses the cost and effectiveness of the architecture, which could potentially fall under the categories of Cybersecurity (cs.CYBER) and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
